# Figma — Pantallas por JTBD (design-file)

Aplica al montar o editar flujos en **[MyOwnTrip_design-file](https://www.figma.com/design/Vf2tNMXyKAlJSV53A1v4Is/MyOwnTrip_design-file)** (`Vf2tNMXyKAlJSV53A1v4Is`).

